&lt;p&gt;Band 5 Cardiac Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ward 6 Cardiology - Birmingham Heartlands Hospital&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ward 9 Cardiology – Birmingham Heartlands&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ward 23 Cardiology - Good Hope Hospital Cardiac&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Catheter Suite (Cross Site)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a dynamic, fast moving, innovative cardiac centre with a passion for providing safe care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You may be newly qualified, experienced in cardiology or just fancied a new challenge. If you have enthusiasm, commitment and can work as part of a team to deliver exceptional care then we want you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer you excitement, development and a chance to be your very best. Not to mention being part of a great supportive team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It takes a certain person to be able to work in this environment and we need motivated, passionate and hardworking individuals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you feel this is an opportunity for you then please call us, visit us or apply now.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information please contact Ward Manager Sharyne Nickolds on 0121 424 3218.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates will be shortlisted and interviewed on a continuous basis for convenience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At University Hospitals Birmingham we support flexible working and welcome applications from nurses seeking flexible working opportunities and family friendly working hours.&lt;/p&gt;
